  <brief_title>Arthrodesis Versus Extra-articular Plate Fixation in Lisfranc Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>Arthrodesis Versus Extra-articular Bridge Plating of the First Tarsometatarsal Joint After Acute Lisfranc Injury</official_title>
  <sponsors>
