  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare arthrodesis of the first TMT-joint to extraarticular
      bridge plate fixation of the same joint in acute Lisfranc injuries.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We want to compare arthrodesis of TMT 1 to temporary bridge plating of TMT 1 in acute
      Lisfranc injuries where at least tarsometatarsal joints 1-3 are involved.

      We preform arthrodesis of TMT 2 and 3 in both groups.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
